data.description: Welcome to your dream home at 48 Satilla Sands Dr, a charming brick residence that combines the serenity of country living with the convenience of proximity to town. This delightful property is now available for sale and offers a perfect blend of comfort, style, and functionality.     This house features four generously sized bedrooms and three full bathrooms, catering to both privacy and convenience. The layout includes a split floor plan that ensures a peaceful retreat for all members of the household. The upstairs bonus room, complete with a full bath, provides flexible space that can easily serve as a fourth bedroom or whatever your needs may be.    The heart of this home is the family room, adorned with vaulted ceilings and a cozy gas fireplace, creating an inviting atmosphere for gatherings or quiet evenings in. The kitchen boasts stainless steel appliances, ample cabinet space, and an eat-in area, making meal preparation and dining both enjoyable and comfortable. A separate area off the living room can be tailored to your lifestyle as a formal dining room or office.    Step outside to discover the large fully fenced private backyard, offering plenty of room for outdoor activities or future pool installation. The covered back porch provides an ideal setting for relaxation or entertaining guests.    Additional highlights include a spacious master suite with dual vanities and garden tub, laundry room with washer and dryer included, security system, and irrigation system.    This property represents an exceptional opportunity to enjoy the best of both worlds - tranquil country ambiance with easy access to town amenities. Don't miss out on making 48 Satilla Sands Dr your new home!
